column2: SELECT    nt.id_noAGN, nt.RA, nt.DEC, nt.Z, nt.FIBERID as fiber_id, nt.MJD as mjd_, nt.PLATE as plate_,    n.objid, n.distance, n.type,     p.ra AS pra, p.dec AS pdec, p.modelmag_r,    s.specobjid, s.bestobjid, s.z as sz,     s.mjd, s.plate, s.fiberID,		    pz.z as photoz, pz.zErr, pz.photoErrorClass as Class,    pz.absMagu,pz.absMagg,pz.absMagr,pz.absMagi,pz.absMagz,    sm.mstellar_median,    abs(nt.Z-pz.z) as zdif INTO #tt FROM MyDB.ControlLERG AS nt    OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(nt.RA, nt.DEC, nt.R) AS n    LEFT JOIN PhotoObj AS p ON n.objid=p.objid    LEFT JOIN SpecObj as s ON n.objid=s.bestobjid   LEFT JOIN Photoz as pz ON n.objid=pz.objid   LEFT JOIN stellarMassPCAWiscBC0# as sm ON s.specobjid=sm.specobjid WHERE pz.z > #.   GO  SELECT tt.* FROM #tt as tt WHERE tt.zdif<#   and #<tt.Class   and tt.Class<# ORDER BY tt.id_noAGN INTO MyDB.ControlVecLERG
